    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant restoration or can be used for parts. The engine currently struggles to stay running and has a noticeable knock, while the transmission shifts roughly. Externally, there is substantial rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, and the paint is peeling across the hood and roof. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional dashboard cluster. It is being sold strictly as-is and will likely need to be towed from the lot.",
