    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable driver. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical results of responsible daily use. The body panels are straight, and the alloy wheels are in excellent shape with plenty of tire tread remaining. Inside, the cabin has been kept smoke-free and clean. The leather seating shows only light softening on the driver's bolster, and all interior electronics\u2014including the premium sound system, navigation, and dual-zone climate control\u2014operate perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in great health; it starts up immediately, idles smoothly, and the transmission shifts through all gears without hesitation. Recent service records show consistent oil changes and a cooling system flush. This is a solid, honest car that is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
